<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE topic PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Topic//EN" "topic.dtd">
<topic id="ordered-lists">
  <title>Ordered Lists</title>
  <body>
    <p>Two separate ordered lists must each start at one.</p>
    <ol id="ordered-restart-a">
      <li><p>First ordered item in the first list.</p></li>
      <li><p>Second ordered item in the first list.</p></li>
    </ol>
    <p>A paragraph separates the lists.</p>
    <ol id="ordered-restart-b">
      <li><p>First ordered item in the second list.</p></li>
      <li><p>Second ordered item in the second list.</p></li>
    </ol>
    <p>Nested ordered levels must use deterministic numbering and indentation.</p>
    <ol id="ordered-nested">
      <li>
        <p>Level one item.</p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p>Level two item.</p>
            <ol>
              <li><p>Level three item.</p></li>
            </ol>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li><p>Level one sibling item.</p></li>
    </ol>
  </body>
</topic>
